  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a clay pot over medium-high heat.",
    "add the garlic and cook until fragrant.",
    "add the shrimp and cook until pink.",
    "add the bell pepper and onion and cook until tender.",
    "add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the chicken broth, white wine, black pepper, and salt. stir to combine.",
    "bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 10 minutes.",
    "stir in the fresh parsley and serve the shrimp hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
